<p>New dormers in the existing roof allow the sun to get into the rooms, in addition to providing beautiful views of the forest. The sunroom at the back of the house is upgraded to a new terrace with double glass walls allowing for a cosy covered room with an outdoors feeling. A new room with a private bathroom and storage/wardrobe provides a new flexible space for guests, hobbies or work. This room is located on top of the new covered garage with capacity for up to two cars.</p>

